---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Acceptable Use Policy - intent solutions io">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-900 py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-12">Acceptable Use Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none">
        <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg mb-8">
          Last updated: October 9, 2025
        </p>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">1. Purpose</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            This Acceptable Use Policy ("Policy") governs your use of Intent Solutions IO services, including the HUSTLE youth sports tracking survey and application. By using our services, you agree to comply with this Policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">2. Prohibited Activities</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You may not use our services to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights of others</li>
            <li>Transmit harmful, abusive, or harassing content</li>
            <li>Impersonate any person or entity</li>
            <li>Collect or harvest personal information without consent</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt our services or servers</li>
            <li>Attempt unauthorized access to our systems</li>
            <li>Distribute viruses, malware, or other malicious code</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">3. Youth Data Protection</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Given that our services collect information about youth athletes, we have additional requirements:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">COPPA Compliance:</strong> Parents and guardians must provide verifiable consent before submitting information about children under 13</li>
            <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">GDPR Compliance:</strong> We comply with GDPR requirements for processing children's personal data</li>
            <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Data Minimization:</strong> Only provide information necessary for the survey's stated purpose</li>
            <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Privacy Protection:</strong> Do not share identifying information about minors without proper authorization</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">4. Survey Participation Guidelines</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When participating in our HUSTLE survey:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Provide truthful and accurate information</li>
            <li>Do not submit duplicate responses to manipulate results</li>
            <li>Respect the privacy of other participants</li>
            <li>Do not share personal information of minors without proper consent</li>
            <li>Use the survey for its intended purpose only</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">5. Content Standards</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            All content submitted through our services must:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Be respectful and professional</li>
            <li>Not contain offensive, abusive, or discriminatory language</li>
            <li>Not include spam, advertising, or promotional material</li>
            <li>Not violate privacy or confidentiality obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">6. Enforcement</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We reserve the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Remove or refuse any content that violates this Policy</li>
            <li>Suspend or terminate access to our services for violations</li>
            <li>Report illegal activities to appropriate authorities</li>
            <li>Take legal action to protect our rights and the safety of others</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">7. Reporting Violations</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you become aware of any violation of this Policy, please contact us immediately at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed ml-4">
            <strong class="text-zinc-100">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:jeremy@intentsolutions.io" class="text-zinc-100 underline hover:text-white">jeremy@intentsolutions.io</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We may update this Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">9. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            For questions about this Policy, please contact:
          </p>
          <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed ml-4 space-y-2">
            <p><strong class="text-zinc-100">Intent Solutions IO</strong></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:jeremy@intentsolutions.io" class="text-zinc-100 underline hover:text-white">jeremy@intentsolutions.io</a></p>
            <p>Website: <a href="https://intentsolutions.io" class="text-zinc-100 underline hover:text-white">intentsolutions.io</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-700">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            By using our services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this Acceptable Use Policy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
